race.comment: JUST SUBLIME (1) resumed this grade and did about what expected. Brought strong form to that and won her only second-up outing. Well placed to win with the benefit of the 3kg claim. Stablemate WHATYOUTALKINBOUT (2) led and won her Maiden easily at his second race start and is sure to build on that. He will jump and run from the inside barrier and the in-form Fiore stays in the saddle. A player. CHIPILLY (5) from the same yard has been around the mark without winning. Has an awkward barrier but rates well enough to say she's a chance. EVERLASTING SPIRIT (4) resumes and has won fresh. Maps well and she'll be around the mark if presented on song.
